ActPooled Registered Pension Plans Act
SubjectPooled Registered Pension Plans Regulations
PrecisPOOLED REGISTERED PENSION PLANS REGULATIONS in order to implement the federal portion of the framework for the establishment and administration of Pooled Registered Pension Plans which will be professionally administered defined contribution pension plans targeted to employees and self-employed persons who do not have access to a workplace pension plan.
